high_descs: Go to the right and cross the room to stand in front of the white table.
Pick the knife up from the table.
Turn around and go to the left to face the sink.
Put the knife in the sink and turn it on and then off and pick the knife back up again.
Move to the left and face the drawer to the left of the sink.
Put the knife in the drawer and shut it.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean knife in a drawer.

high_descs: Walk forward, then hang a right and walk over to the white table to the right of the oven.
Pick up the large metal knife off of the table.
Turn around and walk forward, then hang a left and walk up to the sink.
Put the large metal knife in the sink and turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn off the water and remove the now clean knife.
Turn around and walk towards the wall, then hang a right and walk towards the white table, turn right to face the counter to the left of the sink.
Open the leftmost upper drawer and put the clean knife inside then close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean metal knife in a drawer.

high_descs: Hang a right at the silver container in front of the white table and cross the room to a large white table ahead.
Pick up the knife with a yellow handle in front of the toaster on the table.
Turn around and walk to the sink on the left side.
Put the knife inside the sink to the left of the bowl, rinse it off and pick it back up.
Turn around, walk towards the small white table and turn around to face the cabinets under the counter.
Put the rinsed knife inside the drawer on the left side and close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed knife in a drawer.
